<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="cut-v">cut <strong><em>v</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /kʌt/    美 /kʌt/  </p>
<p>(cut, cut)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-vt-vi">1.★ <strong>vt &amp; vi 切 (下)；割 (下)；剪 (下)；砍：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>cut and paste
剪贴</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She cut the apple in half.
她把苹果切成两半。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The material <strong>cuts</strong> easily <strong>with</strong> scissors.
那种材料用剪刀很容易剪断。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He <strong>cut</strong> some fur <strong>from</strong> the family cat to make a brush.
他从家猫身上剪下了一些毛做画笔。</p><footer>2017 浙江</footer></div>

<h4 id="2-vt-vi">2.★ <strong>vt &amp; vi 割伤；割破；划破：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She cut her finger on a piece of glass.
一块玻璃把她的手指割伤了。。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The knife is extremely sharp! Mind you don’t <strong>cut yourself</strong>.
那把刀非常锋利，当心别把自己划伤了。</p></div>

<h4 id="3-vt">3.★ <strong>vt 剪短；修剪：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I <strong>had my hair cut</strong> short.
我把头发剪短了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I was just going to cut my rose bushes but someone had done it.
我正打算修剪我的玫瑰丛，但发现已经有人修剪完了。</p><footer>2010 湖南</footer></div>

<h4 id="4vt">4.<strong>vt 雕刻；凿出：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She cut the carrot to look like a flower.
她把胡萝卜雕成花的形状。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The chair is <strong>cut from</strong> the trunk of a tree.
这把椅子是用一根树干凿成的。</p></div>

<h4 id="5vt">5.<strong>vt 打断；停止；和...绝交：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Japan cut diplomatic ties with the country.
日本与那个国家断绝了外交关系。</p></div>

<h4 id="6-vt-reduce">6.★ <strong>vt 削减；缩减；减少 (reduce)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The store cut the price of winter clothing by 20%.
那家商店冬装降价20%。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Cutting carbon has an immediate effect as costs drop.
减少碳排放量的直接效果就是降低成本。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="cut-back">cut back</h3>
<p>1.<strong>缩减；削减</strong><br />
 to reduce the amount, size, cost etc. of sth：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Several companies are <strong>cutting back on</strong> staff at the moment. 
目前，有几家公司正在裁员。</p></div>

<h3 id="cut-down">cut down</h3>
<p>1.★ <strong>砍倒：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Deserts are also created because people cut down trees and dig up grass.
人们伐树掘草，也会造成土壤沙化。</p><footer>外研③ – 4</footer></div>

<p>2.★ <strong>减少；缩减</strong><br />
to reduce the amount of sth：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The car industry cut down production.
汽车制造商减少了产量。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If you want to lose weight you have to <strong>cut down on</strong> fatty foods.
如果你想减肥就得少吃高脂食物。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We need to <strong>cut</strong> the article <strong>down to</strong> 1,000 words.
我们需要把这篇文章缩减至1000词。</p></div>

<h3 id="cut-in">cut in</h3>
<p>1.<strong>插嘴；打断：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’m sorry to <strong>cut in on</strong> you, but there are one or two things I don’t understand.
抱歉打断你的话，但是我有一两处不大明白。</p></div>

<p>2.<strong>强行超车：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She cut in a red car, forcing the driver to brake heavily.
她强行超到一辆红色的车的前面，迫使那位司机急刹车。</p></div>

<h3 id="cut-off">cut off</h3>
<p>1.<strong>切掉；切断；[常用于被动语态] 使隔绝：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>One of his fingers was cut off in the accident.
他的一根手指在事故中被切掉了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The water supply has been cut off temporarily because the workers are repairing one of the main pipes. 
由于工人们正在维修其中一条主管道，供水暂时被切断。</p><footer>2013 天津</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Finally he reached a lonely island which was completely cut off from the outside world. 
最终，他到达一个完全与外界隔绝的孤岛。</p><footer>2013 山东</footer></div>

<h3 id="cut-out">cut out</h3>
<p>1.<strong>剪下；(从文字作品、文章中) 删掉；剪出：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I cut this article out of the newspaper.
我从报纸上剪下了这篇文章。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Cut out the part about racial prejudice.
删掉有关种族歧视的那部分内容。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She cut out a dress of some old material for me.
她用旧布料为我裁出一件连衣裙。</p></div>

<h3 id="cut-up">cut up</h3>
<p>1.<strong>切碎；割碎；剪碎：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Cut up the carrots before you put them into the pot.
把胡萝卜切碎后放入锅内。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>When their children lived far away from them, these old people felt cut <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ from the world.   （2016 浙江改）  </li>
<li>My uncle hasn’t been able to quit smoking, but at least he has cut <strong><em>_</em></strong>_.   （2013 陕西改）  </li>
<li>I was just talking to Margaret when Jackson cut <strong><em>_</em></strong>_.  （2005 湖南改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. off  2. down  3. in  </p></div>